name: Unidentified Fishing Object
description:
Made in 72 hours for Mini Jam 91

Theme: UFO

Limitation: Fish as a mechanic

You are an "Unidentified Fishing Object" and must go to different planets to collect fish to add to your fish collection. Use your UFO beam to pull the fish out of the water and bring them to space, but watch out, birds are in the sky are they are hungry. Can you collect every type of fish?

Controls:

W and D/Left and Right Arrows - Move UFO beam and navigate menu

Enter/Space - Confirm menu choice
